<h4 id="array-representaion">Array Representaion</h4>

<h4 id="rule">Rule</h4>
<ol>
  <li>if a Node is at index $i$</li>
  <li>its left child is at $2*i$</li>
  <li>its left child is at $2*i+1$</li>
  <li>its parent is at $i/2$</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="linked-list-presentation-of-tree">Linked list presentation of Tree</h4>
<ol>
  <li>we can based on the position relationship between parent and child, to create
a tree.</li>
</ol>
